{{Infobox book | name = Spendors and Glooms | image = File:Schlitz_Splendors_and_Glooms_cover.jpeg | caption = | author = [[Laura Amy Schlitz]] | country = United States | language = English | genre = Fantasy | publisher = [[Candlewick Press]] | pub_date = 2012 | media_type = Print | pages = 400 pp | isbn = 0763669261 | oclc = | dewey = | congress = | preceded_by = | followed_by = }} '''''Splendors and Glooms''''' is a 2012 [[children's novel]] written by [[Laura Amy Schlitz]]. The book was awarded a 2013 [[Newbery Honor]] for excellence in children's literature.<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.ala.org/alsc/awardsgrants/bookmedia/newberymedal/newberyhonors/newberymedal|title = Newbery Honor and Medal Books|date = 2014|website = ALSC|publisher = Association for Library Service to Children|last = |first = }}</ref>
==Critical reception== Critics have noted ''Splendors and Glooms'' to be an "intriguing and imaginative tale"<ref>https://mail.lagcc.cuny.edu/viplogin/default.aspx?redirect=http://search.ebscohost.com/login.aspx?direct=true&db=a9h&AN=86875067&site=ehost-live</ref> and a "not-to be-missed gothic thriller".<ref>http://eds.b.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdfviewer/pdfviewer?sid=8009b441-f077-4721-a8ec-9147382cbaa6%40sessionmgr114&vid=14&hid=104</ref> "The language is rich and lively, and Schlitz, exhibiting the delicate control of a puppeteer of words, even pulls off comic cockney."<ref>http://eds.b.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdfviewer/pdfviewer?sid=8009b441-f077-4721-a8ec-9147382cbaa6%40sessionmgr114&vid=22&hid=104</ref> "The plot is rich with supernatural and incredibly suspenseful elements. Fans of mystery, magic, and historical fiction will all relish this novel."<ref>http://eds.b.ebscohost.com/ehost/pdfviewer/pdfviewer?sid=8009b441-f077-4721-a8ec-9147382cbaa6%40sessionmgr114&vid=25&hid=104</ref>
